  "title": "Brand Ambassador/Corporate Brand",
  "description": "<h2>Job Purpose</h2><p>The Brand Ambassador / Corporate Brand Executive supports the development, execution, and governance of corporate branding initiatives to strengthen brand equity, ensure consistent brand representation, and enhance stakeholder engagement across multiple touchpoints.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities </h2><h3>Brand Management & Brand Governance</h3><ul><li><p>Support the implementation of corporate brand strategies in alignment with organisational objectives</p></li><li><p>Ensure consistent application of brand identity and brand guidelines across all communication channels</p></li><li><p>Assist in maintaining brand standards for marketing and corporate materials</p></li></ul><h3>Marketing Communications & Content Coordination</h3><ul><li><p>Contribute to the development and coordination of corporate marketing and branding content</p></li><li><p>Assist in managing messaging consistency across internal and external communications</p></li></ul><h3>Events & Campaign Support</h3><ul><li><p>Support the planning and execution of branding campaigns, corporate events, exhibitions, and roadshows</p></li></ul><h3>Brand Performance & Market Awareness</h3><ul><li><p>Support basic tracking of brand visibility and engagement metrics</p></li><li><p>Provide inputs to improve branding strategies and execution</p></li></ul><h3>Skills</h3><ul><li><p>Brand Management</p></li><li><p>Marketing Communications</p></li><li><p>Content Coordination</p></li><li><p>Presentation and Interpersonal Skills</p></li></ul><h3>Other Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Strong verbal and written communication skills</p></li><li><p>Professional presence and confidence in engaging diverse audiences</p></li><li><p>Ability to work collaboratively across teams</p></li></ul>",
